              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "DECAY"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " .Irradiated Am-243 sample was cooled for one",
                "       month after irradiation in order that Am-244-m",
                "       and Am-244-g were decayed into Cm-244, then",
                "       dissolved with 3M H-N-O3. Reaction rate was",
                "       measured from Cm-244 alpha activity"
              ]
            }
